OL,7,FA Wiltshire Police officer sent
OL,8,F"abhorrent" racist messages to a
OL,9,Fcolleague in a WhatsApp group chat, it
OL,10,Fhas been revealed.
OL,12,FPC Mark Giles was given a final
OL,13,Fwritten warning after a hearing at
OL,14,FHeadquarters found his behaviour
OL,15,Famounted to gross misconduct.
OL,17,FThe one-day hearing, held last Monday
OL,18,F29 January, and chaired by an
OL,19,FIndependent Legally Qualified Chair,
OL,20,Ffound his actions breached the
OL,21,FStandards of Professional Behaviour.
