OL,7,FThese standards for police officers
OL,8,Finclude authority, respect and
OL,9,Fcourtesy, equality and diversity and
OL,10,Fdiscreditable conduct.
OL,12,FIn April, PC Giles, who was a firearms
OL,13,Fofficer, sent inappropriate, racist
OL,14,Fmessages to a Whatsapp group used by
OL,15,Fthe team he worked in.
OL,17,FThe messages were directed towards
OL,18,Fanother officer which could cause
OL,19,Foffence given his ethnicity.
