OL,7,FDeputy Chief Constable Craig Dibdin
OL,8,Fsaid: "PC Giles' actions fell well
OL,9,Fbelow the high standards of
OL,10,Fprofessionalism that we, and the
OL,11,Fpublic, expect from all police
OL,12,Fofficers, staff and volunteers.
OL,14,F"When details of his behaviour were
OL,15,Freported to us, he was immediately
OL,16,Fsuspended from his role and an
OL,17,Finvestigation commenced.
